text: Dominique Ravoux (5 April 1878 - 5 December 1950) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1878 births Category:1950 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Loire
